<h1>Course Reserves Item</h1>
<% if @map.hours_location.nil? %>
  <p>Oops, it appears that a system error has occurred. Please contact <a href="mailto:lsupport@princeton.edu">
    Library Systems support staff (L-Support)</a> with details so we can get the item to you.</p>
<% else %>
<p>Copies of this item are available at the
  <a href="http://library.princeton.edu/<%= @map.hours_location.code %>/services/course-reserves">
  reserve location in the <%= @map.hours_location.label %></a>. Please contact the circulation desk
  in the <%= @map.lib.label %> with additional questions.</p>
<% end %>
